Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.13,0:01:56.97,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}涌上心头的 感动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:07.06,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}沐浴着湛蓝的阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:11.42,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你迎风前行的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.74,0:02:18.10,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}让我陶醉时 目光相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.22,0:02:22.96,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们齐声欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:30.23,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}就像那 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:37.01,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\an3}无论何时 都想挥动双手的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.89,0:02:41.30,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}确实是 曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:46.83,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}与你同在的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:51.18,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}永远如 小小漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:03:00.97,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}我们的前方 道路在延伸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.39,0:03:09.70,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}攀上 下一个陡坡后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:14.46,OPCH,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)}我们再相见吧
